%^BOLD%^MAGENTA%^ULINE%^Draconic Bloodline%^RESET%^

At some point in your familyâ€™s history, a dragon interbred with your bloodline, and now its ancient power flows through your veins.

%^MAGENTA%^BOLD%^Bloodline Arcana:%^RESET%^
You gain the Draconic Blood feat, allowing you to choose your dragon blood type. When casting spells of the element associate with your bloodline, you gain +1 damage per damage die rolled (essentially equal to your clevel). The draconic elements are as follows:

Red/Gold/Brass     : Fire
Black/Green/Copper : Acid
Blue/Bronze        : Electricity
White/Silver       : Cold

%^MAGENTA%^BOLD%^Power of Wyrms (L31):%^RESET%^
Your form becomes infused with draconic power, granting you immunity to your associated draconic bloodline element. You also gain leathery dragon wings and are considered flying for the purposes of commands like wing.

%^MAGENTA%^BOLD%^Bonus Bloodline Skill%^RESET%^: none

%^MAGENTA%^BOLD%^Bonus Spells%^RESET%^: armor, resist energy, dispel magic, fear, mind fog, true seeing, spell turning, frightful aspect, overwhelming presence
